Short Description: 

Tailor your tour package to match your preferences, including destinations, activities, accommodations, and more for a personalized experience.

Description:

Create your dream travel experience by tailoring every aspect of your tour package to suit your preferences. With the Customize Package feature, you can personalize key elements such as destinations, accommodations, activities, and transport options. Choose your ideal itinerary, include or exclude specific attractions, and set the pace of your journey. Whether you want a luxury retreat, an adventurous exploration, or a family-friendly itinerary, this field empowers you to design a package that aligns perfectly with your needs and interests. Make your trip truly unique and memorable with this flexibility at your fingertips.

Terms & Conditions:

  • Customization Scope:
    The customization feature allows travelers to personalize specific aspects of their tour packages, including destinations, activities, accommodations, and transportation, subject to availability and feasibility.
  • Booking Confirmation:
    All customized packages are subject to approval and confirmation from our team. Requests will be reviewed, and a final itinerary will be shared for confirmation before booking.
  • Pricing and Payment:
    • The total cost of a customized package may vary based on selections and will be communicated in the final quote.
    • Prices are subject to changes due to market fluctuations, exchange rates, or unforeseen circumstances.
    • Full payment must be made prior to confirmation as per the payment schedule provided.
  • Amendments and Changes:
    • Modifications to the package after confirmation may incur additional charges.
    • Requests for changes are subject to availability and feasibility at the time of the request.
  • Cancellation Policy:
    • Cancellations will be handled as per the standard cancellation policy of the application.
    • Refunds, if applicable, will depend on the cancellation timeline and the terms agreed upon during booking.
  • Travel Documentation:
    The traveler is responsible for ensuring all necessary travel documents, including passports, visas, and permits, are valid and up-to-date for the destinations chosen.
  • Third-Party Services:
    Some parts of the package (e.g., flights, hotel stays, guided tours) may be provided by third-party vendors. The application is not liable for delays, cancellations, or issues arising from third-party services.
  • Liability:
    • The application will not be held responsible for events beyond its control, including natural disasters, political unrest, or other force majeure circumstances.
    • Travelers are encouraged to purchase travel insurance to cover unforeseen incidents.
  • Health and Safety:
    • Travelers are advised to disclose any medical conditions or special needs that may affect their travel experience.
    • The application is not liable for health issues or accidents during the trip unless explicitly covered under the selected package.
  • Validity of Offers:
    Customized package proposals are valid for a limited period, as specified during the booking process. Delayed responses may result in changes to availability or pricing.
  • Personal Information:
    All personal data provided during the customization process will be handled according to the application’s privacy policy and used solely for the purpose of trip planning and booking.
  • Acceptance of Terms:
    By confirming a customized tour package, the traveler acknowledges and agrees to abide by these terms and conditions.
